attributes.description:
The Ford Ranger is a fantastic bakkie, with exceptional build quality, a roomy interior and is one of the smoothest driving bakkies on the road. The 2.2L common-rail turbocharged diesel engine is a gem, combining great power, with better than average fuel consumption. This particular Ranger has been exceptionally well cared for, and conveniently been equipped with a tonneau cover, tow bar, roll bar and smash n grab safety film.

Balance of Ford’s factory warranty for 4 years / 120’000kms, as well as the 5 years / 90’000km service plan.

Don't miss out. Call us now, or leave your details and we will be sure to call you.

Finance Can Be Arranged, Nationwide Delivery, Trade-ins Welcome, Full Service History.

Price Excludes Documentation and Registration Costs. E&OE

As one of the many Motus Select Pre-owned dealerships, we pride ourselves in excellent service and offer vehicles that can be trusted and enjoyed. Customer satisfaction is our main priority! 

MOTUS: Live, Love, Drive.
